<plot>Luna Sea wants to make it as an actor. Trudy wants to make her film about 'the larger lady'. In pursuing their goals, Trudy and Luna find out a lot about themselves and the people they thought they knew. This film takes a satirical look at the world of showbiz and film making. Many stereotypes are confronted, but all with a lightly humourous touch.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?384315</url></doc>
